CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Operating through consolidated subsidiaries in the PRC, ZJK Industrial is a high-tech enterprise specializing in manufacturing and sale of precision fasteners, structural parts and other precision metal parts products for new energy vehicles and intelligent electronic equipment, such as mobile phones, smart watches, drones, and 5G communication base stations. Our main products include various standard screws, nuts, bolts, turning parts, stamping parts and Computer Numerical Control machining parts. Due to our technology, product quality and ability to develop new products, we've become a supplier for some well-known enterprises and their original equipment manufacturers in industries such as consumer electronics and new energy vehicles. We have both China-based and overseas sales teams in North America. In addition, the Company has established a factory in Vietnam in April 2024 and plans to open a sales office in the United States in early 2025.
